I will use my blade to
share this with the world.
dictionary.summon:
I've waited so very
long for this moment.
I devote myself to you.

leader skill.desc: 광속성 유닛으로부터 피해 데미지 10% 감소
leader skill.name: 빛의 수호

bb.desc: 적 전체에게 광속성 7연속 데미지
bb.name: 발키리 템페스트

dictionary.description: A war goddess who wielded her sword in the name of divine justice. The gods revealed that her mission was to destroy all evil. She was called the goddess of victory as she always won when fighting with the blessing of the gods. Many soldiers prayed to her before battle, though she was neutral during the war. Today, she still helps Summoners, but no one yet knows her true motive.
dictionary.evolution:
I can hear the gods.
My mission is to fight
with you.
dictionary.fusion:
Thank you.
I will lead you to
absolute victory.
dictionary.summon:
The time has come!
Time to raise my sword!
Onward to battle!

leader skill.desc: 광속성 유닛으로부터 피해 데미지 10% 감소
leader skill.name: 빛의 수호

bb.desc: 적 전체에게 광속성 8연속 데미지
bb.name: 스타라이드 레이

dictionary.description: A goddess who worked hard to save humans when the gods invaded. However, she sided with them not out of compassion, but because she knew siding with them would allow her to fight an even stronger foe. She kept notes on all the strongest gods, humans, and beasts. However, what happened to those written in Jona's notes is unknown.
dictionary.evolution:
There is a light that only
shines in the middle of battle.
Let me show you this light!
dictionary.fusion:
You seem a worthy ally.
I'd appreciate it if you wouldn't
mind helping me out sometime.
dictionary.summon:
My name is Jona.
I was born to fight!
Let's bask in victory's glory!

leader skill.desc: 광속성 유닛으로부터 피해 데미지 15% 감소
leader skill.name: 빛의 결계

bb.desc: 적 전체에게 강력한 광속성 14연속 데미지＆아군의 BB게이지 상승
bb.name: 스타 크루세이드

dictionary.description: This goddess is the living manifestation of war, known as Legendary Jona's true form while on the battlefield. Her motives are plain and simple: challenging the strong means everything. Records state that she fought to save the human race, but this is not completely true. The reason being that as soon as she had finished bringing down a powerful god, she then pointed her sword at a human hero. The blade that had once carried the hopes of the human race would now bring despair instead.
dictionary.evolution:
Battle and battle to the bitter end.
Fighting is living.
I shall teach this to you.
dictionary.fusion:
Thanks for the offerings.
However, what I really want
is to fight you now.
dictionary.summon:
Let us run around the battlefield
and bask in the glory of victory!
Come, we leave immediately!

leader skill.desc: 광속성 유닛으로부터 피해 데미지 15% 감소＆턴 경과 후 대폭 BB게이지 증가
leader skill.name: 창세광신의 결계

sbb.desc: 적 전체에게 강력한 광속성 17연속 데미지＆아군의 BB게이지 상승＆3턴간 아군 전체의 BB게이지 서서히 증가
sbb.name: 엑세리온

bb.desc: 적 1명에게 광속성 5연속 데미지＆BC HC출현률 상승
bb.name: 홀리 레이

dictionary.description: A pistoleer from another world that appeared on the outskirts of the ruined La Veda Republic. It's said he was a town sheriff. In Grand Gaia he continued eliminating villains with his other-worldly pistol, defending the justice he believed in. Children imitated him aiming his gun, saying, "I judge the evil the law can't reach."
dictionary.fusion:
I accept this strength,
and promise to use it to
protect the people.
dictionary.summon:
How rare, a Summoner!
Hey, take me with you.
I'll bring my pistol along.

leader skill.desc: 모든 유닛의 공격력 10% 상승
leader skill.name: 맹자의 힘

bb.desc: 적 1명에게 광속성 10연속 데미지＆BC와 HC 출현율 상승
bb.name: 스타 칠드런

dictionary.description: A pistoleer from another world active on the outskirts of the ruined La Veda Republic, Heidt defeated villains with his lone pistol, and came to be known as the Holy Marksman. Women loved him, but he refused them , so it was said he likely had a wife back in his home world. He fought hard in the war, yet his death was not recorded. Rumor is that he had returned to his world.
dictionary.evolution:
Fine, I'll show you.
Show you how to use
a pistol, that is!
dictionary.fusion:
You think I need more power?
Alright, I'll get even stronger!
dictionary.summon:
Holy Marksman?
Nah, I'm just a pistoleer.
I'll come with, if that's OK.

leader skill.desc: 모든 유닛의 공격력 15% 상승
leader skill.name: 왕자의 힘

bb.desc: 적 1명에게 광속성 11연속 데미지＆BC HC출현률 상승
bb.name: 스타 버스터

dictionary.description: A pistoleer from another world active on the outskirts of the ruined La Veda Republic. As the war grew in intensity, Heidt disappeared for a period of time. He eventually returned, brandishing a massive gun, and with a confident devil-may-care smile on his face he said, "Ha ha ha. I was scolded for not having properly finished what I came here to do!" It's said that no one since has been able to match his superior shooting skills.
dictionary.evolution:
Evolution is easy, you know.
All it takes is a kind word from a girl
to motivate a man to improve himself.
dictionary.fusion:
Hey now!
Is that all you've got?
Let's give it a little more!
dictionary.summon:
Guns can be used for different reasons.
Some are good and some are bad.
How do you plan to use mine?

leader skill.desc: 모든 유닛의 공격력 20% 상승
leader skill.name: 패왕의 힘

bb.desc: 적 1명에게 광속성 20연속 데미지＆BC와 HC 출현율 상승
bb.name: 스타 게이저

dictionary.description: A gunner who made his living in the La Veda Republic. After a defeat from the God Army seemed imminent during the great war, he wondered the outskirts of town searching for anyone who hadn't been able to evacuate. Those who were rescued by Heidt often wished to fight by his side, helping him to rescue a great number of people. Even after finding out that the people he had saved were convicted criminals, Heidt did not hold it against them. The only thing he ever mentioned about them was written in a letter to his wife, which read that he "had been pointing his gun towards the wrong enemy the whole time."
dictionary.evolution:
If the gods are enemies,
then neither justice nor evil exists.
So I will create justice of my own!
dictionary.fusion:
Heh, a drink before battle,
and another after victory.
There's nothing better!
dictionary.summon:
Guns and humans can be used
for justice or for evil.
You should use your power well too!

leader skill.desc: 모든 유닛 공격력 25%상승＆암속성 유닛으로부터 피해 데미지 15% 감소
leader skill.name: 암신의 위광

sbb.desc: 적 전체에게 광속성 20연속 데미지＆BC와 HC 출현율 상승＆아군 전체에게 2턴간 방어력 무시 공격 부여
sbb.name: 메테오 스트림

bb.desc: 적 전체에게 랜덤으로 광속성 4연속 데미지
bb.name: 드래곤 보이스

dictionary.description: A fairly common dragon in Grand Gaia. They're often seen on clear days, leisurely weaving through the clouds. They don't have interest in humans and don't get involved unless necessary. With a strong sense of justice rarely seen among dragons, they bring terror to those they deem evil, regardless of species. The wyvern's roar makes those with evil souls hide in fear.
dictionary.fusion:
My intentions are just.
How about yours?
dictionary.summon:
Can you handle this mission?
Then show me, just how much
can humans bear.

leader skill.desc: BB게이지 상승량 대폭  상승
leader skill.name: 전쟁신의 빛

bb.desc: 적 전체에게 랜덤으로 광속성 5연속 데미지
bb.name: 제노사이드 블래스터

dictionary.description: Among the many dragons, there is a giant, extremely powerful dragons that go by the name Bahamut. They swoop down and suppress conflicts and disputes between other dragons. Their judgement is always fair, and no one ever objects. When someone has been judged to have harmed nature, Bahamut passes divine punishment as a representative of all dragons.
dictionary.evolution:
I will be the signpost
that lights your path.
dictionary.fusion:
If you hold justice within you,
you can use my strength as you will.
dictionary.summon:
The gods have alread decided.
I am the will of this world.
Can you bear the earth's will?

leader skill.desc: BB게이지 상승량 대폭  상승
leader skill.name: 전쟁신의 빛

bb.desc: 적 전체에게 랜덤으로 강력한 광속성 6연속 데미지
bb.name: 천룡포 테스타먼트

dictionary.description: The strongest and highest ranked in the history of all dragons, Rameldria engaged in many battles with many beings, even gods. This can be traced back to myths from long ago. None who lost to Rameldria were recorded as having survived, and it's believed that when the world is on the verge of abyssal despair, its tremendous power will return once again.
dictionary.evolution:
So you've come to fight.
Let my strength be your
weapon.
dictionary.fusion:
Can you hear the angry
voice of the planet?
dictionary.summon:
I can feel your intention.
If you're really planning on
exceed the heavens, I'll help.

leader skill.desc: BB게이지 증가량 크게 상승
leader skill.name: 전쟁신의 위광

bb.desc: 적 전체에게 랜덤으로 강력한 광속성 8연속 데미지
bb.name: 홀리 블래스터

dictionary.description: Recorded in legend, Rameldria was said to be one of the strongest of all the dragons, though few know the legend didn't stop there. In a few remaining stories it is told that Rameldria, once thought to be invincible, was actually once defeated by a human. Instead of being embarrassed by this, Rameldria instead showed respect toward the human. Then, having been accepted by the humans, with a bright flash of light it evolved into Duelmex.
dictionary.evolution:
I am the great Duelmex.
My power exists to purify
this world!
dictionary.fusion:
I may have friends,
but no one stands in my way!
I will obliterate all enemies!
dictionary.summon:
Death to all who do wrong
and have no value to society!

leader skill.desc: BB게이지 증가량 대폭 상승
leader skill.name: 전쟁신의 패광

sbb.desc: 적 전체에게 강력한 광속성 10연속 데미지＆확률로 마비 효과
sbb.name: 스타더스트 플레어

bb.desc: 적 전체에게 광속성 2연속 데미지
bb.name: 갤럭시 배럿

dictionary.description: A knight from the ruined La Veda Republic, history books say he was the only one who fought against the world's destruction until the very end. He was known as the strongest warrior in the Veda cavalry. People wanted to know if he was stronger than Atro, but legend claims he didn't care, saying, "What would it matter?"
dictionary.fusion:
Strength is always necessary,
even in something as simple
as keeping one's faith.
dictionary.summon:
Are you worthy of me
dedicating my sword to you?
Let me measure your worth.

leader skill.desc: 광속성 유닛의 공격력 25% 상승
leader skill.name: 광신의 힘

bb.desc: 적 전체에게 강력한 광속성 4연속 데미지
bb.name: 세이크리드 포스

dictionary.description: A knight from the ruined La Veda Republic. He resisted the world's destruction until the very end. He is excellent at the sword, and great as a commander. His tactics steadily wore down his enemies. Deeply trusted by his soldiers, after a soldier proclaimed, "I know not if he's stronger than Atro, but he is most definately more overwhelming!" he harshly rebuked that soldier.
dictionary.evolution:
My sword is full of light!
This is evolution!
dictionary.fusion:
We need strength to save
the world. I feel very
strongly about that.
dictionary.summon:
This light... Who are you?
I swear by my sword that I will save the world. Let's go!

leader skill.desc: 광속성 유닛의 공격력 50% 상승
leader skill.name: 창세광신의 힘

bb.desc: 적 전체에게 강력한 광속성 6연속 데미지
bb.name: 아스트랄 노바

dictionary.description: A knight from the ruined La Veda Republic who resisted the world's destruction until the very end. He anticipated the human loss at an early stage of the war, and in order to delay it he implemented a strange tactic, using a smaller forces to take on larger armies. The strategy was promising, but Will struggled until the end, knowing humanity would ultimately lose.
dictionary.evolution:
In this new form,
I will save the world!
dictionary.fusion:
We need strength to save
the world. I feel very
strongly about that.
dictionary.summon:
Oh, great light!
Grant this Summoner glory
and victory!

leader skill.desc: 광속성 유닛의 공격력 50% 상승
leader skill.name: 창세광신의 힘

bb.desc: 적 전체에게 강력한 광속성 7연속 데미지
bb.name: 이슈타르 번

dictionary.description: A knight of the La Veda Republic that fought against the world's destruction until the very end. Charged by Lucius was saving the world, he deciding to give up command and return to being a lone knight. Informing his subordinates to follow Lucius' commands, he equipped himself with various sacred items before taking on the gods by himself. Free from the responsibility of command, Will, and the soldiers who decided to follow him anyway, cut down countless gods.
dictionary.evolution:
How vain a form.
Power should exist as a means
to carry out one's will.
dictionary.fusion:
I don't know if there's anything
left to protect anymore.
Still, I will never give up!
dictionary.summon:
You who dare defy fate.
Let us fight together!
We can decide the future!

leader skill.desc: 광속성 유닛의 공격력 50% 상승&턴 경과로 BB게이지 증가
leader skill.name: 광채신의 힘

sbb.desc: 적 전체에게 강력한 광속성 10연속 데미지＆HC 출현율 대폭 상승
sbb.name: 아발론

bb.desc: 적 전체에게 강력한 광속성 14연속 데미지&아군 전체의 HP 대폭 회복&3턴간 BC와 HC 출현율 상승
bb.name: 이슈타르 캘리버

dictionary.description: A knight who fought against the world's destruction until the very end. As he continued to fend off the invading God Army, a knight appeared before him. This knight had been a fellow villager who had sworn his allegiance to the gods. When the knight asked Will why he kept fighting if there was no one left for him to protect, Will answered that someone in need of his power may appear, and therefore he had to make sure to survive until the end. He then drew his sword anew as the last living human in Grand Gaia.
dictionary.evolution:
The curse cast upon Grand Gaia
has turned into hope. This is
my reward for fighting faithfully!
dictionary.fusion:
I have no one left to protect.
Nevertheless, I'll continue fighting.
That's what I've chosen.
dictionary.summon:
There is nothing as cruel
as being left with a snip of hope.
I want to ease his suffering someday.

extra skill.desc: BB 및 SBB에 3턴간 광속성 부여하는 효과 추가&「신기」 장비 시 전투 중에 모든 능력 20% 상승
extra skill.name: 미래에 바치는 힘

leader skill.desc: 광속성 유닛의 공격력 100% 상승&턴 종료 후 대폭 BB게이지 증가
leader skill.name: 광성개신의 힘

sbb.desc: 적 전체에게 강력한 광속성 35연속 데미지&3턴간 아군 전체의 HP 서서히 회복&공격BB의 공격력 상승 효과 부여
sbb.name: 로엔그린

ubb.desc: 적 전체에게 아주 강력한 광속성 22연속 데미지(남은 HP가 많을수록 위력 상승)&1턴간 공격력과 방어력 초대폭 저하&2턴간 암속성 유닛에게 받는 데미지 초대폭 감소
ubb.name: 앨비언

dictionary.description: A small nymph thought to be born from light, one of the six elements made by the gods. It's mischievous and likes startling travelers in the dark with a blinding light. It's popular with Summoners for its ability to give special powers to others, but it hates being captured and only goes along with those it likes. There are also unvalidated rumors that it can be malicious at times.
dictionary.summon:
I am a Light Nymph, pew!
You seem interesting.
Lemme go with you, pew!

dictionary.description: A spirit that rules light, one of the six elements created by the gods. The light from its body is luminous enough to brighten any dark place. However, since the light it emits is so strong, it is difficult to look at it for a long time. It worries about this and is often irritated by it. Legends has it that people who receive strength from Light Spirits have their dormant powers awoken.
dictionary.summon:
Pew, pew, pew!
So annoying, pew!
Just fuse me already, pew!

dictionary.description:
Worshipers of light gave this miraculous stone idol life through prayer. It's said that the holy power it holds can call forth mysterious powers sleeping in all life.
Its discoverer was attracted to its divinity, got too close and then took a severe blow from it. It's called the "light-beard giant" since beams of light are seen emitting from its mouth.
dictionary.summon:
I am a Light Idol.
It seems you know my purpose.
I will go with you.

dictionary.description: Created by the gods, it embodies light's power. Legend is that those whom the great gods deem worthy can gain their power. Its huge wings sparkle in seven colors, and it's said to be an omen as it appears during auroras. The Light Totem is the gods' executor, not handing down judgments itself, but instead appearing after a decision has already been made.
dictionary.summon:
I am a Light Totem.
You would be wise to use my
godly powers responsibly.

dictionary.description: A monster that shimmers all over. It likes eating gemstones, but as it can't digest them it instead stores them inside itself. It is often referred to as a moving treasure chest. Many Summoners try to capture them, but they're fast and not very common. One must be proficient in finding them to be able to capture one. It, the Jewel King and the Jewel God are classified as jewel types.
dictionary.summon:
I am a Jewel Ghost!
I twinkle beautifully, don't I?
Let's be friends!

dictionary.description: A bigger, hungrier version of a Jewel Ghost. Since the gems it eats also remain inside of it, it is highly valued, even more so than the Jewel Ghost. Some Summoners search them out in order to get rich quick, but they are usually ruined by searching expenses. They are sometimes called foolish, and are often subject to ridicule.
dictionary.summon:
Oh, I'm full.
Hmm? You have more for me?
Then I guess I'm hungry again!

dictionary.description: A jewel type monster that is even larger and even more voracious than the Jewel King. Not only does it hold the gems it's eaten in its body, but those gems also merge together producing even more precious jewels making it is even more valuable than the others. Naturally, there are many Jewel God related crimes, there being a high number of counterfeits, abductions, and scams.
dictionary.summon:
I can still eat.
Give me more gems, please!
My belly is bottomless!

dictionary.description: A jewel type monster that makes even a Jewel God look tiny. Its existence had been rumored since long ago, but there were many who didn't believe in its existence nowadays. Contrary to Jewel Gods, it fuses the precious jewels it ingests and makes beautiful stones unlike anyone has ever seen. It has so many precious stones in its stomach that their glow is manifested even in its outer appearance. One can sell this god for a lot of money, but to buy one, one must be a millionaire.
dictionary.summon:
Are you gonna feed me?
I'm a glutton,
so you better prepare yourself!

bb.desc: 적 전체에게 광속성 4연속 데미지
bb.name: 브레이브 에지

dictionary.description: A swordswoman from the ruined La Veda Republic. Traveling the world with her adventurer parents since childhood helped her easily surpass most other swordsmen. However, the day after she turned 16, her parents disappeared, leaving her an old ring and a letter reading, "Head for the legendary ancient ruins." She immediatlely set out on her solo journey with nothing more than an old ring and the letter her parents left.
dictionary.fusion:
Fusion is great.
With it it's so easy to
get back my strength.
dictionary.summon:
A Summoner, eh?
I guess I can help a little!
And I'll be watching you!

bb.desc: 적 전체에게 광속성 5연속 데미지
bb.name: 브레이브 임팩트

dictionary.description: A swordswoman from the ruined La Veda Republic, she was known as an adventurer who traveled around ancient ruins in search of her parents. Her adventures, like when she vanquished an evil spirit, or her times travelling through unexplored jungles, inspired her. More than glory, she just wanted to find her parents.
dictionary.evolution:
Haha, I've gotten stronger!
Now take me somewhere
more exciting!
dictionary.fusion:
Don't think this is
all I've got. I have a
lot more stored up inside.
dictionary.summon:
Wanna go on an adventure?
Great! Let's have some fun!

leader skill.desc: 턴 종료 후 대폭  BB게이지 증가
leader skill.name: 힘의 고동

bb.desc: 적 전체에게 광속성 7연속 데미지
bb.name: 스타더스트 폴

dictionary.description: A swordswoman from the ruined La Veda Republic. She found her parents at some ancient ruins, but her joy was short lived. They had blocked the ruins' destructive power by binding themselves to them. Ignoring their pleas to be allowed to suppress the power with their lives, Alma defeated it herself. Her adventures ended, and she was known soforth as a hero for both preventing a catastrophe and for saving her parents.
dictionary.evolution:
Come with me!
With my strength we can go
anywhere you want to!
dictionary.fusion:
My power is overflowing!
My strength has returned along
with all my memories!
dictionary.summon:
I've been waiting for you!
Let's start our adventure
to save the world!

leader skill.desc: 턴 종료 후 대폭  BB게이지 증가
leader skill.name: 힘의 고동

bb.desc: 적 전체에게 광속성 8연속 데미지
bb.name: 화이트 에스페란자

dictionary.description: A swordswoman from the La Veda Republic. After her travels ended and she'd saved her parents, they all went back to their hometown for the first time in a long time. However, their peaceful days were brought to an end by the invasion of the gods, at which time they left as a family to protect the people. During the intense battle Alma's mastered her sword technique, though her parents displayed even greater mastery and strength. At first Alma was surprised to see this, but eventually she just smiled as she continued her piercing attack.
dictionary.evolution:
A new adventure!
Alright, let's get going!
I'm waiting!
dictionary.fusion:
It's time to train.
I want to be able to surprise
my mother and father.
dictionary.summon:
What do you think?
I'm a quick learner, eh?
Are you surprised?

leader skill.desc: 턴 종료 후 BB게이지 크게 증가
leader skill.name: 신격의 고동

bb.desc: 적 전체에게 광속성 14연속 데미지

dictionary.description: A swordswoman from the La Veda Republic. As a knight of La Veda, Alma fought to protect everyone in and out of her reach. Thanks to the many friends they made during their travels, Ark felt a new power awakening within him. Seeing that another man was attempting to use his own body as a blockade against the attack to buy the refugees more time to escape, Nevsky silently made his way towards him, joining his blockade with his arms stretched out beside him. There are no records left stating what happened to him following this, but the fact that many refugees were able to make it safely to Elgaia may be proof that his attempt to protect them was successful.

Ha ha ha!

I look forward to more!

dictionary.description: A famous adventurer and world traveler, and father to Alma. Known for his great strength, he left his footmarks around the globe while he explored with his beloved axe in hand, defeating even the most atrocious beasts with one blow. However, due to his ridiculous strength, his axe broke after continuous use. He is also famous for sharing his stories with the local children of the towns he visited. His daughter Alma was also included among them, listening to her father's exploits over and over again.
dictionary.fusion:
Waaahhh!!
I'm overflowing with power!
I have to show this to my daughter.
dictionary.summon:
Is this the setting
for a new adventure?
I can't wait!
My power will come in handy!

dictionary.description: A famous adventurer and world traveler. It is said that he heroically defeated his enemies on the battlefield, and that his decisiveness and awareness were so top class that he was able to avoid any kind of trap in mere seconds. During his travels, a spectacled scholar girl told him about a great destructive power that lay dormant within some ancient ruins. He then decided to head in that direction in order to seal it. However, he was worried about what would become of his daughter. After his wife pleaded that she take them with him, they set off on their journey as a family.
dictionary.evolution:
With this power I can go to
new and unexplored places.
Okay, let's get going!
dictionary.fusion:
I feel more powerful!
Just like after eating
my wife's cooking!
Haha! Did I say too much?
dictionary.summon:
Summoner!
Let's go on a new adventure!
We should prepare as soon as possible!

dictionary.description: A family man and adventurer that set off against the god army in order to help the people. After him and his wife were both saved thanks to Alma's efforts in the ancient ruins, he couldn't have been prouder of how much his little girl had grown. Right after the great war with the gods, he gave a pep talk to his daughter, who refused to change her mind since she was still enveloped in the excitement of great adventure. Thus they set off again together, this time with exceptional cooperation, defeating enemy after enemy. With a smile on his face, Hogar showed his daughter just what he could do with the powerful axe he had discovered within the ruins.
dictionary.evolution:
Summoner!
Look at my axe and power!
I came here itching for an adventure!
dictionary.fusion:
More training for me?
Looks like your enemy
is a pretty big one.
dictionary.summon:
The adventures left behind
are only part of the story.
Only the adventurer knows the truth.

dictionary.description: A knight from the La Veda Republic who gladly went into service for the gods. Having nothing in common with his fellow knights, he always trained himself in order to be of use to the gods. However, it is said that he continuously challenged anyone who dared to disrespect the gods to a duel, believing that his victories were a sign from the gods proving his righteousness. It is said that he had a very peculiar fighting style, repelling all enemy attacks like an impregnable fortress. Finally driving them into a corner, he would force them to regret their lack of faith in the gods.
dictionary.fusion:
How unnecessary...
I can become stronger
through my own will alone!
dictionary.summon:
What a disgrace!
To think that I have to pledge myself
to a Summoner!

dictionary.description: A knight who followed the will of the gods and fought against his own race. When the invasion from the gods started, Narza obliged to the gods' decision to obliterate the human race. After assassinating a high priest who tried to fight against the gods, Narza brought his head to the God Army. Pleased with how Narza had proven himself true, and how he was ready to lose his own life for their cause, the gods put him in charge of the vanguard. It is written that Narza was so moved by this that he happily pointed his sword at his fellow fighters until the day before the battle.
dictionary.evolution:
This power...
The gods! They are near,
are they not?!
dictionary.fusion:
I will offer this power to the gods.
I don't care what becomes of you!
dictionary.summon:
Summoner before me.
If you walk alongside the gods,
I shall pledge my life to you.

dictionary.description: A knight who pledged his life to the gods, vowing to defeat one of the Six Heroes. Identical to his situation, a knight who was serving the God Army while still a human appeared before Narza as a messenger of a certain god. This knight disclosed to Narza the name of a hero who had been repelling attacks from the God Army in various areas. When Narza was told that it was the will of the gods that he slay this hero, he made the godly power wielding Magress his enemy and assaulted him. However, his attack proved futile when Magress's comrades protected him.
dictionary.evolution:
I just heard the voices of the gods!
They tell me to fight,
to defeat my enemies!
dictionary.fusion:
I can feel the gods' power...
Are you...? Could you be...
...a messenger of the gods?!
dictionary.summon:
I can see the light...
The light is pouring on me...
The gods have accepted me.

dictionary.description: The reproduced test unit version of Maxwell, the god that craves destruction and the pillar of the of the Four Fallen Gods. Using compiled research to make her as close to the real goddess as possible, this unit fell behind thanks to either lack of information, or lack of comprehension of the goddess's real power. However, there is no doubt that she is much more powerful than the average unit. Wielding enough power to rebuild Grand Gaia from scratch, this Fallen God could name herself creator of the new world, giving enough of a glimpse as to the type of menace that Maxwell truly represents.
dictionary.fusion:
My wish.
My power, which covers the light...
shall beacon the Fallen Gods.
dictionary.summon:
Child who doesn't fear sin.
My will has already faded.
Thus, let's try following humans instead.

dictionary.description: The all-purpose store "Lawson" appeared suddenly through a loophole in the gate that leads to another world. It is said that once some Summoners tried to visit the store and there was a Metal God dressed in a blue and white striped uniform working inside. Stating that it wanted to try new experiences in order to grow, the Metal God receives his customers with a smile from ear to ear. Unfortunately, even though it has tried new things, its knowledge and skills don't seem to have improved.
dictionary.summon:
Welcome
to Grand Gaia's Lawson!
What's that?
No, you can't heat me up!

dictionary.description: All Summoners are talking about "Lawson," the store with a great variety of products that suddenly appeared from a loophole in the gate. There, one can catch a glimpse of a Crystal God dressed in a blue and white striped uniform. A Summoner who studied this phenomenon stated that he saw the god working hard by organizing the books on the shelves. The Crystal God was quoted as eagerly saying that it would like to use the money it earns to take the other Crystal Gods on a holiday.
dictionary.summon:
Welcome!
For a limited time only,
we have more experience!
Would you like some?

dictionary.description: The all-purpose store "Lawson," where Metal Gods have been spotted working at, appeared through a loophole in the gate that leads to another world. Upon hearing these rumors, the Jewel God decided to start working there too to avoid being considered uncool by its peers. It seems to have grown fond of the blue and white striped uniform it has to wear as well. People who have seen the god working firsthand say that it just stood there staring at all the food on the shelves as if he wanted to eat it. And if it really wanted to, there is no doubt that it could eat all of it...
dictionary.summon:
Do you have your card?
If you collect many points
you can get neat stuff!

bb.name: 프릭션

dictionary.description: Deemo, the mysterious inhabitant of an otherworldly castle and the girl who suddenly fell from the sky. Deemo, who wished to return the girl he'd saved who had fallen from above to the world from which she came, found strange trees growing to the sound of his piano. Then one day, an unfamiliar window suddenly appeared before them. On the other side lied "Grand Gaia," a world unknown to the two of them.
dictionary.fusion:
Our strength has increased.
This feels quite strange.
It's like the music Deemo plays.
dictionary.summon:
Where am I?
This is Grand Gaia, you say?
It seems strange to me.

dictionary.description: An amnesiac girl from the foreign land of Grand Gaia and Deemo, the strange being that saved her. Thinking there may be clues to the girl's past in Grand Gaia, the two decided to go and look. However, they found themselves landing in the middle of a war between the gods and man. Without any other choice, the girl armed herself with a rapier. Together with Deemo, she fought back gods and monsters alike, and it's said the two ventured around to countless villages and came to touch the hearts of many people.
dictionary.evolution:
Your wings are pretty, Deemo.
They're so big and white.
You look even cooler than before!
dictionary.fusion:
What a useful technique you have.
It'd be nice if we could use this
to help our trees grow, too.
dictionary.summon:
So this is Grand Gaia.
I've never been here before!
Is it OK if I look around?

dictionary.description: A beautifully winged young woman holding a divine flower on her right hand, and a chalice on her left. She was first sighted in one of the countless forests in the Vriksha Region. In the beginning, people had considered her a goddess based on her appearance, giving her offerings and the like. But claiming to be a human, she refused all of the offerings, and left the forest. As luck would have it, however, she destroyed an atrocious demon nesting in that region at about the same time, which only made the people's adoration for her even stronger.
dictionary.fusion:
How peculiar that you would share
your power with me. However, I have
enough of my own, thank you.
dictionary.summon:
A Summoner?
Please, keep your distance.
I don't think I can meet your expectations.

bb.name: 홀리 브레스

dictionary.description: A beautifully winged young woman holding a divine flower on her right hand, and a chalice on her left. Disliking being revered by people as a goddess, she moved from forest to forest until she one day decided to head towards the Sea of Aldahlia. There, she heard rumors of a mad god troubling Aldahlian citizens by creating storms. Afterwards, the storms in Aldahlia ceased thanks to her efforts, though it is said that she never mentioned a word of this to anyone.
dictionary.evolution:
The water flowing from this chalice
comes from deep within the heart.
Let's purify your memories.
dictionary.fusion:
Your message has been received.
I shall show you my gratitude
through my future actions.
dictionary.summon:
I don't want to get myself involved...
People always pry into my life.
But you may be different...

bb.name: 홀리 그레이스

dictionary.description: A beautifully winged young woman holding a divine flower on her right hand, and a chalice on her left. There are many legends that seek to describe her true identity, but the most influential of these states that she was a descendant of the Aldahlian sea god's lover. The divine flower, chalice, and wings she had in possession all held a power unknown to mankind, which is why many scholars believe these were gifts granted to her by the sea god himself. There is little evidence to support that at this moment, but there is no one in existence who questions the power she once held.
dictionary.evolution:
Ahh...
I've changed, haven't I?
I shall pledge myself to you.
dictionary.fusion:
I am so happy.
So happy that someone supports me.
Can I place my trust in you?
dictionary.summon:
Unique blood flows through my veins.
My power also comes from this.
Do you believe me?

dictionary.description: The queen of a small country in the Bariura region. Her kingdom was suddenly destroyed by an ancient dragon. Excelling as a swordswoman as well, she survived this tragic situation, remembering the last words the late king had uttered whilst she stared at the piles of rubble before her. "It is your royal duty to protect the people." With those words in mind she wished not for vengeance, but fought to save her people instead. However, on her travels she met a knight thirsting for revenge, and though she did not sympathize with this, they still managed to cooperate.
dictionary.fusion:
How much power do you seek?
Revenge only leads to more revenge.
Forget the past, face the future!
dictionary.summon:
Tell me of your pain.
I shall save you from it.
It is my duty as royalty.

leader skill.desc: 모든 상태이상에 대폭  저항
leader skill.name: 청정의 광풍

bb.name: 스파이럴 샤인

dictionary.description: The queen of a small country in the Bariura region which was destroyed by an ancient dragon. She set off to find the dragon not to take revenge, but to defeat it in order to prevent it from causing any further damage. After failing to persuade the dragon and subsequently being hurt by the creature, more companions joined the queen and the knight in their journey. Along with a disciple and a former disciple, her support and that of her comrades helped to change the knight's mind. It is said that after witnessing this she felt the need to keep a strong disposition, but simultaneously somewhat lonely.
dictionary.evolution:
This power...
I have finally been acknowledged...
If this is true, I shall not let you down!
dictionary.fusion:
I wish to become stronger...
For my own sake as well...
Oh, pardon me. I said nothing...
dictionary.summon:
I have an unseemly side as well.
Will you still accept me?
Then, I shall become your sword!

leader skill.desc: 모든 상태이상 무효화
leader skill.name: 창궁의 신풍

bb.name: 크리스털 미라주

dictionary.description: The queen of a ruined country in the Bariura region. When her and her comrades challenged the dragon once more, she approached the creature more closely than what was necessary, and drew her sword. It is speculated that she did this because she was frustrated with her lack of power when compared to her comrades. Finding herself in a bind due to her thoughtless action, the queen was protected by Shera, allowing her to escape. Ashamed of herself, she fought till the open gate swallowed everything whole, though not for her own selfish reasons. She fought for her friends, and for her people.
dictionary.evolution:
Thank you...
I was finally able to forgive myself.
I am now all yours.
dictionary.fusion:
I will not doubt myself any longer!
I believe in my own strength!
Shall we? Grant me more power!
dictionary.summon:
Even though I asked him to
suppress his feelings numerous times,
I couldn't do it myself.

sbb.name: 애드벤트 스텔라

dictionary.description: An imp who guided others of his kind during the creation of the heavens and the earth. Said to have been born from the combination of dozens of imps, Arton supervised his subordinates while they worked. Not only is he extremely wise, but as the almighty imp, it is speculated that he could be used as an all-purpose ingredient instead of fusing numerous other imps at once. However, capturing Arton is an extremely rare feat, and thus research on this subject has failed to advance any further.
dictionary.summon:
It seems you're still incomplete.
I shall help you reach perfection.
Come on, don't be shy now!

bb.desc: 적 전체에게 강력한 광속성 10연속 데미지＆아군 전체에게 2턴간 방어력 무시 공격 부여
bb.name: 미스틴

bb.desc: 적 전체에게 강력한 광속성 25연속 데미지＆아군 전체에게 2턴간 방어력 무시 공격 부여
bb.name: 멜틴타

leader skill.name: 녹금의 궁왕

dictionary.description: A swordsman from another world who faced off against the Demon King Dhaos. The only son of Miguel Albane, a famous swordsman and master of a sword fighting school, Cress took up the sword from a very young age. He lived peacefully in his village until he was 17 years old, when his hometown was suddenly attacked by Dhaos's minions while he and his best friend Chester were away. His village now destroyed, and his parents murdered, Cress left his home vowing to avenge them.
dictionary.fusion:

Why are people born?

You got lucky meeting such a powerful
